1
00:00:01,376 --> 00:00:02,878
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "ENTERPRISE"...</i>

2
00:00:02,878 --> 00:00:05,213
WE ONLY WANT TO BE
YOUR PARTNERS,

3
00:00:05,213 --> 00:00:07,215
TO WORK TOGETHER
IN COMMON CAUSE.

4
00:00:07,215 --> 00:00:08,592
[ EXPLOSION ]

5
00:00:10,678 --> 00:00:13,012
ADMIRAL FORREST
HAS BEEN KILLED.

6
00:00:13,012 --> 00:00:16,642
THE DNA ON THE BOMB'S CONTROLS
WAS LEFT BY THIS WOMAN, T'PAU.

7
00:00:16,642 --> 00:00:18,811
THE ANSWERS YOU NEED
ARE ON VULCAN.

8
00:00:18,811 --> 00:00:23,190
AND HOWEVER FAR YOU HAVE
TO TAKE THIS INVESTIGATION,

9
00:00:23,190 --> 00:00:24,859
YOU HAVE MY SUPPORT.

10
00:00:24,859 --> 00:00:26,735
THIS IS A DESERT CALLED
THE FORGE.

11
00:00:26,735 --> 00:00:30,030
THE ROUTE'S THE ONE SURAK
SUPPOSEDLY FOLLOWED.

12
00:00:32,366 --> 00:00:33,868
THE GUARD RECOGNIZED THE PERSON

13
00:00:33,868 --> 00:00:35,619
WHO BROUGHT IN THE BOMB
WE FOUND IN THE RUBBLE.

14
00:00:35,619 --> 00:00:37,621
-T'PAU.
-NO.

15
00:00:38,789 --> 00:00:41,000
-IT WAS YOU.
-WHAT'S A<i> KATRA?</i>

16
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:44,753
SYRRANNITES CLAIM IT'S
THE ESSENCE OF A VULCAN MIND,

17
00:00:44,753 --> 00:00:47,255
THAT IT CAN BE TRANSFERRED
FROM THE BODY BEFORE DEATH.

18
00:00:47,255 --> 00:00:49,842
V'LAS WAS INVOLVED
WITH THE ATTACK ON YOUR EMBASSY.

19
00:00:49,842 --> 00:00:52,928
HE'S RESPONSIBLE FOR BLAMING IT
ON THE SYRRANNITES.

20
00:01:12,740 --> 00:01:14,783
BEFORE WE ANNOUNCE
OUR DECISION,

21
00:01:14,783 --> 00:01:18,161
IS THERE ANYTHING
YOU WISH TO SAY?

22
00:01:18,161 --> 00:01:19,872
MY ACTIONS WERE TAKEN

23
00:01:19,872 --> 00:01:23,458
IN THE BEST INTEREST OF VULCAN
AND THE HIGH COMMAND.

24
00:01:23,458 --> 00:01:27,004
KEEPING SECRETS FROM US
IS IN OUR BEST INTEREST?

25
00:01:27,004 --> 00:01:29,882
HAD I REVEALED
MY ABILITIES AS A MELDER,

26
00:01:29,882 --> 00:01:32,968
MY YEARS OF SERVICE
WOULD NOT HAVE BEEN POSSIBLE.

27
00:01:32,968 --> 00:01:35,429
YOUR ACCOMPLISHMENTS
HAVE BEEN NOTEWORTHY.

28
00:01:35,429 --> 00:01:37,472
THEY DON'T JUSTIFY DECEPTION.

29
00:01:37,472 --> 00:01:40,559
DECEPTION HAS NEVER BEEN
A STRANGER TO THIS ROOM.

30
00:01:41,476 --> 00:01:43,062
I CAUTION YOU.

31
00:01:43,062 --> 00:01:45,022
ONE OF OUR OWN MEMBERS
WAS RESPONSIBLE

32
00:01:45,022 --> 00:01:46,774
FOR BOMBING THE EARTH EMBASSY,

33
00:01:46,774 --> 00:01:49,944
AN ACT WE TRIED TO
BLAME ON THE SYRRANNITES.

34
00:01:49,944 --> 00:01:52,237
THAT ASSESSMENT WAS CORRECT.

35
00:01:52,237 --> 00:01:55,616
OUR INVESTIGATION OF STEL
HAS REVEALED HE'S A SYRRANNITE.

36
00:01:55,616 --> 00:01:58,493
I FIND THAT
DIFFICULT TO ACCEPT.

37
00:01:58,493 --> 00:02:01,371
NUMEROUS DOCUMENTS
WERE DISCOVERED IN HIS HOME.

38
00:02:01,371 --> 00:02:03,290
THE EVIDENCE IS IRREFUTABLE.

39
00:02:03,290 --> 00:02:05,000
SYRRANNITES WERE RESPONSIBLE,

40
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,377
AND THEY'LL BE DEALT WITH
ACCORDINGLY.

41
00:02:07,377 --> 00:02:09,504
REGARDING THE MATTER AT HAND,

42
00:02:09,504 --> 00:02:13,050
YOUR POSITION IS TERMINATED
IMMEDIATELY.

43
00:02:13,050 --> 00:02:15,594
YOU'RE TO SURRENDER
ALL CLASSIFIED MATERIALS

44
00:02:15,594 --> 00:02:18,179
TO THE SECURITY DIRECTORATE
BEFORE LEAVING.

45
00:02:18,179 --> 00:02:23,435
I REMIND YOU THAT YOUR
LOYALTY OATH IS STILL IN EFFECT.

46
00:02:23,435 --> 00:02:25,186
VIOLATION OF THAT OATH --

47
00:02:25,186 --> 00:02:27,522
-I'M AWARE OF THE PENALTY.
-GOOD.

48
00:02:27,522 --> 00:02:32,193
IS THERE ANYTHING
ELSE YOU'D LIKE TO SAY?

49
00:02:32,193 --> 00:02:36,323
THERE'S A GREAT DEAL THAT NEEDS
TO BE SAID, EXCELLENCY,

50
00:02:36,323 --> 00:02:38,993
BUT NO ONE'S
WILLING TO LISTEN.

51
00:02:40,577 --> 00:02:45,373
♪ IT'S BEEN A LONG ROAD ♪

52
00:02:45,373 --> 00:02:48,460
♪ GETTING FROM THERE TO HERE ♪

53
00:02:48,460 --> 00:02:52,506
♪ IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME ♪

54
00:02:52,506 --> 00:02:56,135
♪ BUT MY TIME IS FINALLY NEAR ♪

55
00:02:56,135 --> 00:03:00,597
♪ AND I WILL SEE MY DREAM
COME ALIVE AT LAST ♪

56
00:03:00,597 --> 00:03:04,267
♪ I WILL TOUCH THE SKY ♪

57
00:03:04,267 --> 00:03:08,229
♪ AND THEY'RE NOT GONNA
HOLD ME DOWN NO MORE ♪

58
00:03:08,229 --> 00:03:10,899
♪ NO, THEY'RE NOT GONNA
CHANGE MY MIND ♪

59
00:03:10,899 --> 00:03:14,028
♪ 'CAUSE I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

60
00:03:14,028 --> 00:03:15,988
♪ OF THE HEART ♪

61
00:03:15,988 --> 00:03:19,574
♪ I'M GOING WHERE MY HEART
WILL TAKE ME ♪

62
00:03:19,574 --> 00:03:24,496
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH TO BELIEVE ♪

63
00:03:24,496 --> 00:03:26,874
♪ I CAN DO ANYTHING ♪

64
00:03:26,874 --> 00:03:31,628
♪ I'VE GOT STRENGTH
OF THE SOUL ♪

65
00:03:31,628 --> 00:03:34,506
♪ AND NO ONE'S GONNA BEND
OR BREAK ME ♪

66
00:03:34,506 --> 00:03:40,345
♪ I CAN REACH ANY STAR ♪

67
00:03:40,345 --> 00:03:41,930
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

68
00:03:41,930 --> 00:03:44,474
♪ I'VE GOT, I'VE GOT, I'VE GOT ♪

69
00:03:44,474 --> 00:03:47,936
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

70
00:03:47,936 --> 00:03:52,149
♪ FAITH OF THE HEART ♪

71
00:04:18,592 --> 00:04:19,718
WHO ARE YOU?

72
00:04:19,718 --> 00:04:21,720
I'M JONATHAN ARCHER.

73
00:04:22,679 --> 00:04:25,640
CAPTAIN OF THE EARTH VESSEL.

74
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:28,102
AND YOU MUST BE T'POL.

75
00:04:33,232 --> 00:04:35,358
YOU ARE A LONG WAY
FROM<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

76
00:04:35,358 --> 00:04:39,487
I'M HERE TO FIND THE PERSON
WHO BOMBED THE EARTH EMBASSY.

77
00:04:40,488 --> 00:04:42,116
HER NAME IS T'PAU.

78
00:04:43,533 --> 00:04:45,493
AND SHE LOOKS
A HELL OF A LOT LIKE YOU.

79
00:04:45,493 --> 00:04:47,537
I AM T'PAU.

80
00:04:47,537 --> 00:04:50,999
YOU MURDERED MY FRIEND,
ALONG WITH 40 OTHER PEOPLE.

81
00:04:50,999 --> 00:04:54,544
I HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH
THE DESTRUCTION OF YOUR EMBASSY.

82
00:04:54,544 --> 00:04:55,963
THE EVIDENCE SAYS YOU DID.

83
00:04:57,297 --> 00:05:00,425
I HAVEN'T LEFT THIS DESERT
FOR 2 YEARS.

84
00:05:00,425 --> 00:05:02,719
WHAT DOES THAT TELL YOU
ABOUT YOUR EVIDENCE?

85
00:05:02,719 --> 00:05:04,054
IT TELLS ME THAT YOU'RE LYING.

86
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:07,599
YOU HAVE A LOT TO LEARN
ABOUT SYRRANNITES.

87
00:05:07,599 --> 00:05:09,601
YOU HAVE A LOT TO LEARN
ABOUT HUMANS.

88
00:05:09,601 --> 00:05:12,771
WE DON'T SIT BACK AND DO NOTHING
WHILE OUR PEOPLE ARE ATTACKED.

89
00:05:12,771 --> 00:05:14,189
NO, YOU TRAVERSE
VAST WASTELANDS,

90
00:05:14,189 --> 00:05:16,733
BASED ON FALSE INFORMATION.

91
00:05:19,402 --> 00:05:22,697
WHAT DID YOU PLAN TO DO
WHEN YOU FOUND ME --

92
00:05:22,697 --> 00:05:24,032
PLACE ME UNDER ARREST?

93
00:05:24,032 --> 00:05:25,867
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

94
00:05:25,867 --> 00:05:29,288
IT SEEMS EVERYTHING I'VE HEARD
ABOUT YOUR SPECIES IS ACCURATE.

95
00:05:29,288 --> 00:05:30,705
MOTHER.

96
00:05:32,582 --> 00:05:34,626
I'M PLEASED TO SEE
THAT YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

97
00:05:34,626 --> 00:05:39,173
WE HAVE A GREAT DEAL
TO TALK ABOUT.

98
00:05:39,173 --> 00:05:42,341
-AGREED.
-YOU TOLD THEM
WHERE TO FIND US.

99
00:05:42,341 --> 00:05:45,386
-YES.
-IS THERE ANYONE
ELSE WITH YOU?

100
00:05:45,386 --> 00:05:47,346
NO.

101
00:05:47,346 --> 00:05:49,683
TO HAVE CROSSED THE FORGE
BY YOURSELVES

102
00:05:49,683 --> 00:05:52,435
WITH THE SANDFIRE STORMS
THIS TIME OF YEAR?

103
00:05:52,435 --> 00:05:55,730
WE MET A SYRRANNITE.
HE HELPED US FIND SHELTER.

104
00:05:55,730 --> 00:05:56,898
WHO WAS THIS PERSON?

105
00:05:58,566 --> 00:05:59,776
HIS NAME WAS AREV.

106
00:06:01,111 --> 00:06:04,323
HE WAS STRUCK DOWN
BY AN ELECTRICAL CHARGE.

107
00:06:04,323 --> 00:06:05,573
HE DIDN'T MAKE IT.

108
00:06:05,573 --> 00:06:06,992
HE'S DEAD?

109
00:06:08,994 --> 00:06:11,121
ARE YOU CERTAIN
HIS NAME WAS AREV?

110
00:06:11,121 --> 00:06:12,873
THAT'S WHAT HE TOLD US.

111
00:06:14,582 --> 00:06:18,086
HIS TRUE NAME WAS SYRRAN.

112
00:06:19,921 --> 00:06:22,507
HE WAS OUR LEADER.

113
00:06:29,848 --> 00:06:32,059
[ DOOR CREAKS ]

114
00:06:36,646 --> 00:06:38,190
[ SIGHING ]

115
00:06:38,190 --> 00:06:41,400
CAPTAIN, ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

116
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:43,070
YEAH, I'M OKAY.

117
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:44,905
[ SIGHS ]

118
00:06:44,905 --> 00:06:48,700
RIGHT BEFORE AREV DIED,
HE GRABBED ME.

119
00:06:48,700 --> 00:06:52,662
HE...PUT HIS HAND
ON MY FOREHEAD.

120
00:06:52,662 --> 00:06:57,000
I FELT SOMETHING
INSIDE...MY HEAD.

121
00:06:58,710 --> 00:07:02,463
DO YOU THINK
HE WAS TRYING TO MELD WITH YOU?

122
00:07:02,463 --> 00:07:04,549
I DON'T KNOW.

123
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:11,265
BUT EVER SINCE,
I HAVEN'T BEEN MYSELF.

124
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:20,440
YOU PUT US ALL IN DANGER.
WHAT IF THEY'D BEEN FOLLOWED?

125
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:22,650
I ONLY WANTED HER TO KNOW
I WAS SAFE.

126
00:07:22,650 --> 00:07:25,862
YOU COULD HAVE ACCOMPLISHED THAT
WITHOUT REVEALING OUR LOCATION.

127
00:07:25,862 --> 00:07:28,156
I CAN'T CHANGE WHAT I'VE DONE.

128
00:07:28,156 --> 00:07:29,741
SHE DOESN'T DESERVE
IMPRISONMENT.

129
00:07:29,741 --> 00:07:31,159
I WANT HER RELEASED.

130
00:07:31,159 --> 00:07:32,911
NOT UNTIL WE'VE CONFIRMED
THEIR STORY.

131
00:07:32,911 --> 00:07:35,038
MY DAUGHTER WOULDN'T LIE.

132
00:07:35,038 --> 00:07:36,957
SHE'S NOT MERELY
YOUR DAUGHTER --

133
00:07:36,957 --> 00:07:38,875
SHE'S A MEMBER OF STARFLEET,

134
00:07:38,875 --> 00:07:41,836
AND STARFLEET IS ALLIED
WITH THE HIGH COMMAND.

135
00:07:41,836 --> 00:07:43,422
THEY'LL BOTH REMAIN
WHERE THEY ARE

136
00:07:43,422 --> 00:07:45,548
UNTIL I'M SATISFIED
THEY CAN BE TRUSTED.

137
00:07:45,548 --> 00:07:46,674
[ ENGINE HUMMING ]

138
00:07:49,303 --> 00:07:52,306
THE SEARCH PATROLS
ARE FLYING DAY AND NIGHT.

139
00:07:52,306 --> 00:07:54,808
THEY'RE THE LEAST
OF OUR WORRIES NOW.

140
00:07:54,808 --> 00:07:57,685
IF SYRRAN IS DEAD...

141
00:07:59,271 --> 00:08:02,816
...THEN EVERYTHING
WE'VE WORKED FOR IS LOST.

142
00:08:06,611 --> 00:08:09,614
I CAN'T BELIEVE
THEY THREW YOU OUT.

143
00:08:09,614 --> 00:08:11,658
JUST BECAUSE YOU HELPED US?

144
00:08:11,658 --> 00:08:13,410
I KNEW THE RISKS.

145
00:08:13,410 --> 00:08:15,370
THERE'S GOT TO BE SOME WAY
YOU CAN FIGHT THIS.

146
00:08:15,370 --> 00:08:18,665
I COULD PROTEST, BUT IT WOULDN'T
ACCOMPLISH ANYTHING.

147
00:08:18,665 --> 00:08:20,917
V'LAS ISN'T ONE
TO CHANGE HIS MIND.

148
00:08:20,917 --> 00:08:22,752
WHO THE HELL PUT HIM IN CHARGE,
ANYWAY?

149
00:08:22,752 --> 00:08:25,464
OUR SOCIETY REWARDS MERIT.

150
00:08:25,464 --> 00:08:30,218
V'LAS HAS DEMONSTRATED
A SINGULAR TALENT FOR GOVERNING.

151
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:34,055
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO NOW?

152
00:08:34,055 --> 00:08:36,557
IF YOU'RE REFERRING
TO MY CAREER,

153
00:08:36,557 --> 00:08:39,227
I HAVEN'T GIVEN IT
MUCH THOUGHT.

154
00:08:39,227 --> 00:08:42,814
THERE'S SOMETHING MORE IMPORTANT
WE NEED TO DISCUSS.

155
00:08:42,814 --> 00:08:45,650
HAVE YOU MADE CONTACT
WITH T'POL OR YOUR CAPTAIN?

156
00:08:45,650 --> 00:08:47,777
WE CAN'T REACH THEM,
AND THEY CAN'T REACH US.

157
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:52,366
V'LAS IS DETERMINED
TO WIPE OUT THE SYRRANNITES.

158
00:08:52,366 --> 00:08:54,201
HE'S PARTICULARLY INTENT

159
00:08:54,201 --> 00:08:57,120
ON DESTROYING
THEIR ENCAMPMENT IN THE FORGE.

160
00:08:57,120 --> 00:09:00,874
WHERE THE CAPTAIN
AND T'POL ARE HEADED.

161
00:09:00,874 --> 00:09:03,043
THEY MAY BE IN GRAVE DANGER.

162
00:09:03,043 --> 00:09:05,962
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

163
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:25,148
YOU MUST HAVE
QUESTIONS FOR ME.

164
00:09:29,194 --> 00:09:31,988
I CAN'T UNDERSTAND HOW YOU COULD
JOIN THESE PEOPLE.

165
00:09:33,865 --> 00:09:35,450
I'VE BEEN GROWING DISILLUSIONED

166
00:09:35,450 --> 00:09:38,619
WITH VULCAN SOCIETY
FOR SOME TIME.

167
00:09:38,619 --> 00:09:40,663
WHEN I WAS FORCED
TO RESIGN FROM THE ACADEMY,

168
00:09:40,663 --> 00:09:45,919
I-I BEGAN SERIOUSLY
TO QUESTION MY BELIEFS.

169
00:09:45,919 --> 00:09:48,505
AND THIS IS WHERE YOU CAME
FOR ANSWERS?

170
00:09:52,175 --> 00:09:54,511
SYRRANNITES BELIEVE

171
00:09:54,511 --> 00:09:57,347
THAT THE VULCANS HAVE STRAYED
FROM THE TEACHINGS OF SURAK.

172
00:09:57,347 --> 00:09:59,099
CONSIDERING
WHAT THE HIGH COMMAND HAS DONE

173
00:09:59,099 --> 00:10:00,600
IN RECENT YEARS --

174
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,936
THE -- THE LISTENING STATION
AT P'JEM,

175
00:10:02,936 --> 00:10:05,480
THE SUPPRESSION OF DISSENT --

176
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:07,648
OUR POSITION
ISN'T SO HARD TO ACCEPT.

177
00:10:09,276 --> 00:10:12,112
YOU COULD HAVE TOLD ME ALL THIS
WHEN I CAME TO VISIT.

178
00:10:12,112 --> 00:10:13,988
THE HIGH COMMAND
WAS JUST BEGINNING

179
00:10:13,988 --> 00:10:16,366
TO HUNT DOWN
SUSPECTED SYRRANNITES.

180
00:10:16,366 --> 00:10:17,825
I WAS AFRAID I WOULD BE NEXT.

181
00:10:17,825 --> 00:10:19,869
I WANTED TO KEEP YOU
OUT OF IT.

182
00:10:19,869 --> 00:10:23,331
I KNOW YOUR MARRIAGE TO KOSS
WAS FOR MY SAKE,

183
00:10:23,331 --> 00:10:25,166
TO HELP ME REGAIN MY POST.

184
00:10:25,166 --> 00:10:27,961
I DON'T WANT YOUR APOLOGIES,
MOTHER.

185
00:10:27,961 --> 00:10:30,422
I WANT YOU
TO COME BACK WITH ME.

186
00:10:36,928 --> 00:10:38,597
I CAN'T DO THAT.

187
00:10:39,639 --> 00:10:41,475
[ SIGHS ]

188
00:10:41,475 --> 00:10:45,312
WHEN YOU GAVE ME THAT MAP,
YOU KNEW I'D TRY TO FIND YOU.

189
00:10:45,312 --> 00:10:46,980
I THOUGHT THAT,

190
00:10:46,980 --> 00:10:49,232
IF YOU COULD SEE WHAT
WE WERE TRYING TO ACCOMPLISH...

191
00:10:49,232 --> 00:10:50,900
THAT I'D UNDERSTAND?

192
00:10:52,735 --> 00:10:54,362
THAT I'D JOIN YOU?

193
00:10:55,655 --> 00:10:57,616
I HELD OUT THAT HOPE, YES.

194
00:10:59,784 --> 00:11:01,453
IT'S POSSIBLE
I WAS BEING FOOLISH.

195
00:11:01,453 --> 00:11:03,330
EXTREMELY.

196
00:11:25,059 --> 00:11:27,354
[ EXPLOSIONS ]

197
00:11:34,152 --> 00:11:36,655
WAR IS TAKING ITS TOLL.

198
00:11:37,947 --> 00:11:39,907
VULCAN IS TEARING ITSELF APART.

199
00:11:39,907 --> 00:11:41,409
WHO ARE YOU?

200
00:11:41,409 --> 00:11:44,078
YOU KNOW WHO I AM, CAPTAIN.

201
00:11:44,078 --> 00:11:45,580
[ EXPLOSION ]

202
00:11:54,047 --> 00:11:56,675
SO MUCH DEATH.

203
00:11:56,675 --> 00:12:01,471
HARD TO BELIEVE THIS WILL BECOME
KNOWN AS THE TIME OF AWAKENING.

204
00:12:01,471 --> 00:12:04,098
THAT WAS 1,800 YEARS AGO.

205
00:12:13,024 --> 00:12:14,775
THIS DOESN'T FEEL LIKE A DREAM.

206
00:12:16,194 --> 00:12:20,532
YOU'RE SEEING THE PAST
THROUGH MY EYES.

207
00:12:23,493 --> 00:12:27,997
SYRRAN DID SOMETHING TO ME
BEFORE HE DIED.

208
00:12:29,082 --> 00:12:30,208
HE CHOSE YOU.

209
00:12:30,208 --> 00:12:32,419
[ CHUCKLES ]

210
00:12:32,419 --> 00:12:34,337
YOU DON'T TRUST VULCANS,
CAPTAIN.

211
00:12:34,337 --> 00:12:38,174
GIVEN YOUR EXPERIENCES WITH
THEM, I CAN'T SAY I BLAME YOU.

212
00:12:39,426 --> 00:12:41,135
THE CULTURE YOU'VE COME TO KNOW

213
00:12:41,135 --> 00:12:43,846
ISN'T THE ONE
I HELPED TO CREATE.

214
00:12:43,846 --> 00:12:45,348
MY PEOPLE HAVE STRAYED,

215
00:12:45,348 --> 00:12:49,143
AND SOMEONE MUST RESTORE THEM
TO THE PATH.

216
00:12:50,895 --> 00:12:53,106
YOU'VE GOT THE WRONG MAN.

217
00:12:53,106 --> 00:12:54,982
SORRY, CAPTAIN.

218
00:12:54,982 --> 00:12:58,403
THERE'S AN EARTH EXPRESSION --
"WE'RE STUCK WITH EACH OTHER."

219
00:12:58,403 --> 00:13:02,031
DON'T FIGHT
WHAT'S BEEN GIVEN TO YOU.

220
00:13:02,031 --> 00:13:07,954
OPEN YOUR MIND AND YOUR HEART,
AND THE WAY WILL BECOME CLEAR.

221
00:13:07,954 --> 00:13:09,122
CAPTAIN.

222
00:13:11,165 --> 00:13:13,000
CAPTAIN.

223
00:13:25,096 --> 00:13:27,056
WE'VE PINPOINTED THEIR LOCATION

224
00:13:27,056 --> 00:13:30,059
NEAR THE NORTHEASTERN BORDER
OF THE FORGE.

225
00:13:30,059 --> 00:13:31,852
HOW ACCURATE
IS THIS INFORMATION?

226
00:13:31,852 --> 00:13:34,063
IT'S BASED ON DATA COLLECTED
BY SEARCH PATROLS.

227
00:13:34,063 --> 00:13:36,357
THEY'VE BEEN CONDUCTING MISSIONS
FOR SEVERAL DAYS.

228
00:13:36,357 --> 00:13:40,153
WE'RE GOING TO BOMBARD
THE CAMP...

229
00:13:40,153 --> 00:13:42,530
WITH PHOTONIC WEAPONS.

230
00:13:42,530 --> 00:13:46,200
OUR GOAL ISN'T TO EXTERMINATE
THESE PEOPLE.

231
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:50,121
OUR GOAL IS TO MAINTAIN ORDER.

232
00:13:50,121 --> 00:13:51,956
THEY'RE IN THE DEEP DESERT.

233
00:13:51,956 --> 00:13:53,874
WHAT POSSIBLE HARM
COULD THEY DO US?

234
00:13:53,874 --> 00:13:56,877
THEY'VE ALREADY DESTROYED
AN EMBASSY.

235
00:13:56,877 --> 00:14:00,089
EVENTUALLY, THEY'RE GOING TO
HAVE TO LEAVE THE FORGE,

236
00:14:00,089 --> 00:14:01,675
AND WHEN THEY DO,

237
00:14:01,675 --> 00:14:04,927
WE CAN APPREHEND THEM
WITH LITTLE OR NO LOSS OF LIFE.

238
00:14:04,927 --> 00:14:09,015
IT'S VERY LIKELY THAT SYRRAN
HIMSELF IS INSIDE THE COMPOUND.

239
00:14:09,015 --> 00:14:11,100
WITH ONE DECISIVE THRUST,

240
00:14:11,100 --> 00:14:15,814
WE CAN CRIPPLE THIS INSURGENCY,
PERHAPS END IT.

241
00:14:15,814 --> 00:14:18,358
WE CAN'T LET AN OPPORTUNITY
LIKE THIS PASS US BY.

242
00:14:18,358 --> 00:14:21,653
A SURGICAL STRIKE
COULD MINIMIZE THE LOSS OF LIFE.

243
00:14:21,653 --> 00:14:25,406
THE GEOMAGNETIC ANOMALIES MAKE
A PRECISION ATTACK IMPOSSIBLE.

244
00:14:25,406 --> 00:14:28,535
THIS IS THE ONLY WAY.

245
00:14:29,869 --> 00:14:32,455
WE'LL BEGIN PREPARATIONS
IMMEDIATELY.

246
00:14:37,084 --> 00:14:39,504
THIS MAN --
DID HE TELL YOU HIS NAME?

247
00:14:39,504 --> 00:14:42,757
HE SEEMED TO THINK
I KNEW WHO HE WAS.

248
00:14:42,757 --> 00:14:45,218
DID YOU?

249
00:14:45,218 --> 00:14:46,636
IT WAS SURAK.

250
00:14:48,847 --> 00:14:50,724
WE BELIEVE YOU.

251
00:14:50,724 --> 00:14:53,059
SYRRAN POSSESSED
THE<i> KATRA</i> OF SURAK.

252
00:14:53,059 --> 00:14:55,019
<i>KATRAS</i> ARE NOTHING MORE
THAN A MYTH.

253
00:14:56,354 --> 00:14:58,732
I USED TO THINK THAT

254
00:14:58,732 --> 00:15:02,151
UNTIL I LEARNED TO OPEN UP
MY MIND TO OTHER POSSIBILITIES.

255
00:15:02,151 --> 00:15:04,945
IF SYRRAN KNEW
HE WAS CLOSE TO DEATH,

256
00:15:04,945 --> 00:15:08,282
HE WOULD HAVE TRIED TO TRANSFER
THE<i> KATRA</i> TO SOMEONE ELSE.

257
00:15:08,282 --> 00:15:09,992
I WAS NEAR HIM WHEN HE DIED.

258
00:15:11,786 --> 00:15:14,330
THERE IS ONLY ONE WAY
TO BE CERTAIN.

259
00:15:14,330 --> 00:15:16,499
I HAVE TO MELD WITH YOU.

260
00:15:16,499 --> 00:15:18,292
I'VE HAD MY FILL
OF MIND-MELDS.

261
00:15:18,292 --> 00:15:21,212
THE PROSPECT
DOESN'T APPEAL TO ME, EITHER.

262
00:15:21,212 --> 00:15:24,006
I'VE NEVER MELDED
WITH A HUMAN BEFORE.

263
00:15:24,006 --> 00:15:28,428
YOUR UNCHECKED EMOTIONS WILL,
NO DOUBT, PROVE DISTASTEFUL.

264
00:15:29,512 --> 00:15:32,640
HOWEVER,
I ASK YOUR INDULGENCE.

265
00:15:48,197 --> 00:15:51,367
MY MIND...TO YOUR MIND.

266
00:15:52,368 --> 00:15:56,122
MY THOUGHTS TO YOUR THOUGHTS.

267
00:15:57,123 --> 00:16:00,418
OUR MINDS ARE MERGING.

268
00:16:00,418 --> 00:16:03,922
-OUR MINDS ARE ONE.
-OUR MINDS ARE ONE.

269
00:16:06,215 --> 00:16:08,927
WE'RE IN THE DESERT.

270
00:16:08,927 --> 00:16:12,513
THERE'S A STORM.

271
00:16:12,513 --> 00:16:16,350
WE FIND REFUGE I-IN A CAVE.

272
00:16:17,393 --> 00:16:19,270
SAND-LIGHTNING.

273
00:16:20,313 --> 00:16:22,690
OUR MINDS ARE NOT ALONE.

274
00:16:22,690 --> 00:16:26,152
THERE'S SOMEONE ELSE HERE
WITH US.

275
00:16:26,152 --> 00:16:28,696
I SENSE HIS PRESENCE.

276
00:16:31,324 --> 00:16:33,785
[ GASPING ]

277
00:16:33,785 --> 00:16:35,495
T'PAU?

278
00:16:37,246 --> 00:16:39,081
HE HAS THE<i> KATRA.</i>

279
00:16:44,295 --> 00:16:47,882
WE CAN TRIGGER A MALFUNCTION IN
THIS SATELLITE'S IMAGING NODE.

280
00:16:47,882 --> 00:16:49,425
IT'LL TAKE 6 MINUTES

281
00:16:49,425 --> 00:16:51,636
FOR THE CENTRAL PROCESSOR
TO CORRECT THE ERROR.

282
00:16:51,636 --> 00:16:53,763
THAT SHOULD BE ENOUGH TIME
TO SLIP THROUGH THE NET.

283
00:16:53,763 --> 00:16:55,890
WON'T THEY WONDER
WHAT CAUSED THE GLITCH?

284
00:16:55,890 --> 00:16:57,851
ERRORS OCCUR FREQUENTLY
NEAR THE FORGE.

285
00:16:57,851 --> 00:17:00,102
IT SHOULDN'T RAISE SUSPICION.

286
00:17:00,102 --> 00:17:01,479
[ BEEPING ]

287
00:17:01,479 --> 00:17:03,731
MIND IF I ASK YOU SOMETHING?

288
00:17:05,650 --> 00:17:08,110
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

289
00:17:08,110 --> 00:17:10,947
I NEVER GOT THE IMPRESSION YOU
CARED THAT MUCH ABOUT HUMANS.

290
00:17:10,947 --> 00:17:12,866
SEEMS LIKE...

291
00:17:12,866 --> 00:17:14,909
YOU WERE ALWAYS FINDING
SOMETHING NEW TO COMPLAIN ABOUT.

292
00:17:14,909 --> 00:17:18,663
I LIVED ON EARTH FOR
MORE THAN 30 YEARS, COMMANDER.

293
00:17:18,663 --> 00:17:20,331
IN THAT TIME,

294
00:17:20,331 --> 00:17:23,918
I DEVELOPED AN AFFINITY
FOR YOUR WORLD AND ITS PEOPLE.

295
00:17:25,252 --> 00:17:27,755
YOU DID A PRETTY GOOD JOB
OF HIDING IT.

296
00:17:28,756 --> 00:17:31,258
-THANK YOU.
-[ BEEPING ]

297
00:17:31,258 --> 00:17:34,345
Launch Bay to
Commander Tucker.

298
00:17:34,345 --> 00:17:36,180
GO AHEAD, TRAVIS.

299
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:38,432
WE SHOULD BE READY
WITHIN THE HOUR.

300
00:17:38,432 --> 00:17:40,100
What about helm control?

301
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:42,311
I'VE RIGGED UP
A STICK-AND-RUDDER SYSTEM.

302
00:17:42,311 --> 00:17:43,980
IT'LL GET US
WHERE WE WANT TO GO,

303
00:17:43,980 --> 00:17:46,065
but I can't promise
a smooth ride.

304
00:17:46,065 --> 00:17:48,108
JUST DON'T TELL MALCOLM
ABOUT THAT PART

305
00:17:48,108 --> 00:17:49,443
UNTIL YOU'RE UNDER WAY.

306
00:17:50,528 --> 00:17:51,863
CENTURIES AGO,

307
00:17:51,863 --> 00:17:54,240
A SET OF<i> KATRIC</i> ARKS
WERE DISCOVERED

308
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:55,366
AT THE P'JEM MONASTERY.

309
00:17:55,366 --> 00:17:57,535
<i>KATRIC</i> ARKS?

310
00:17:57,535 --> 00:17:59,370
POLYCRYSTALLINE VESSELS,

311
00:17:59,370 --> 00:18:04,918
ALLEGEDLY USED BY ANCIENT
VULCANS TO PRESERVE<i> KATRAS.</i>

312
00:18:06,377 --> 00:18:09,213
THEY WERE SCANNED,
ANALYZED.

313
00:18:09,213 --> 00:18:12,383
ONE OF THE SCIENTISTS EVEN
ATTEMPTED TO MELD WITH THEM.

314
00:18:12,383 --> 00:18:16,763
THEY FOUND NOTHING TO INDICATE
THE PRESENCE OF A<i> KATRA.</i>

315
00:18:16,763 --> 00:18:18,848
THE VULCAN SCIENCE ACADEMY

316
00:18:18,848 --> 00:18:21,308
WAS JUST AS SKEPTICAL
ABOUT TIME TRAVEL.

317
00:18:21,308 --> 00:18:23,143
DO YOU REALLY BELIEVE

318
00:18:23,143 --> 00:18:27,774
YOU POSSESS THE LIVING SPIRIT
OF SURAK INSIDE YOU,

319
00:18:27,774 --> 00:18:30,317
A MAN WHO DIED
1,800 YEARS AGO?

320
00:18:31,402 --> 00:18:33,780
NOT WHEN YOU
PUT IT LIKE THAT.

321
00:18:35,239 --> 00:18:38,034
THERE IS A LOGICAL
EXPLANATION.

322
00:18:38,034 --> 00:18:39,953
I'M LISTENING.

323
00:18:41,537 --> 00:18:44,123
SYRRAN MELDED WITH YOU
BEFORE HE DIED.

324
00:18:44,123 --> 00:18:48,586
WHAT YOU'RE EXPERIENCING
IS THE RESIDUE OF HIS THOUGHTS.

325
00:18:48,586 --> 00:18:53,466
SO I'M SUFFERING
FROM A MIND-MELD HANGOVER?

326
00:18:53,466 --> 00:18:56,385
I WOULDN'T CHARACTERIZE IT
QUITE THAT WAY...

327
00:18:56,385 --> 00:18:59,013
BUT, ESSENTIALLY.

328
00:18:59,013 --> 00:19:01,515
IT FEELS LIKE...

329
00:19:02,767 --> 00:19:04,727
...MORE THAN THAT.

330
00:19:04,727 --> 00:19:06,813
YOU HAVE NO BASIS
FOR COMPARISON.

331
00:19:06,813 --> 00:19:10,024
YOU'VE NEVER UNDERGONE
A MIND-MELD BEFORE.

332
00:19:10,024 --> 00:19:12,318
SEEING SURAK
IS ONLY A PART OF IT.

333
00:19:12,318 --> 00:19:15,696
I COULD SWEAR I'VE BEEN HERE
BEFORE, IN THIS SANCTUARY.

334
00:19:15,696 --> 00:19:19,659
IT'S LIKE COMING BACK
TO THE HOUSE YOU GREW UP IN.

335
00:19:19,659 --> 00:19:23,037
SYRRAN SPENT
A GREAT DEAL OF TIME HERE.

336
00:19:25,081 --> 00:19:29,085
LET'S SAY YOU'RE RIGHT,
AND IT WAS JUST A MIND-MELD.

337
00:19:29,085 --> 00:19:32,588
HE STILL PUT SOMETHING
IN MY HEAD...

338
00:19:34,507 --> 00:19:36,342
...AND I WANT IT TAKEN OUT.

339
00:19:37,468 --> 00:19:40,138
IT MAY NOT BE POSSIBLE.

340
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:47,854
WHAT CAN WE DO FOR YOU?

341
00:19:47,854 --> 00:19:49,647
<i>WHERE IS YOUR CAPTAIN?</i>

342
00:19:49,647 --> 00:19:53,109
HE'S INDISPOSED AT THE MOMENT.
CAN I HELP YOU?

343
00:19:53,109 --> 00:19:54,902
<i>THE INVESTIGATION</i>
<i>OF THE EMBASSY BOMBING</i>

344
00:19:54,902 --> 00:19:56,403
<i>IS NEARLY COMPLETE.</i>

345
00:19:57,530 --> 00:19:59,239
YOU HAVE A SUSPECT?

346
00:19:59,239 --> 00:20:01,408
<i>THE EVIDENCE AGAINST HIM</i>
<i>AND THE SYRRANNITES</i>

347
00:20:01,408 --> 00:20:03,410
<i>IS COMPELLING.</i>

348
00:20:03,410 --> 00:20:05,371
<i>THERE'S NO LONGER ANY NEED</i>
<i>FOR YOUR PRESENCE HERE.</i>

349
00:20:05,371 --> 00:20:09,000
IF IT'S ALL THE SAME TO YOU,
WE'D LIKE TO STICK AROUND.

350
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:12,503
WE'D PREFER YOU DIDN'T.
THIS IS AN INTERNAL MATTER.

351
00:20:12,503 --> 00:20:14,338
WE'LL KEEP STARFLEET APPRISED

352
00:20:14,338 --> 00:20:16,507
IF THERE ARE
ANY SUBSEQUENT DEVELOPMENTS.

353
00:20:16,507 --> 00:20:18,217
<i>EXCELLENCY --</i>

354
00:20:18,217 --> 00:20:21,470
AGAIN, YOU HAVE MY DEEPEST
SYMPATHY FOR YOUR LOSS.

355
00:20:21,470 --> 00:20:23,389
<i>ALL OF VULCAN GRIEVES WITH YOU.</i>

356
00:20:23,389 --> 00:20:26,851
WITH ALL RESPECT,
WE AREN'T LEAVING,

357
00:20:26,851 --> 00:20:29,062
NOT UNTIL WE KNOW
EXACTLY WHAT HAPPENED.

358
00:20:29,062 --> 00:20:31,438
<i>I'VE ALSO CONTACTED</i>
<i>ADMIRAL GARDNER.</i>

359
00:20:31,438 --> 00:20:34,650
<i>I'M SURE YOU'LL BE HEARING</i>
<i>FROM HIM SOON.</i>

360
00:20:34,650 --> 00:20:37,444
<i>-A PLEASANT JOURNEY.</i> 
-[ BEEPS ]

361
00:20:37,444 --> 00:20:39,446
THE SON OF A BITCH
HUNG UP ON US.

362
00:20:39,446 --> 00:20:40,907
SHOULD I TRY TO GET HIM BACK?

363
00:20:43,492 --> 00:20:46,412
NO ONE HERE HAS EVER PERFORMED
THIS RITUAL.

364
00:20:46,412 --> 00:20:48,748
I'VE STUDIED IT FOR SOME TIME.

365
00:20:48,748 --> 00:20:50,791
I BELIEVE I CAN CONDUCT IT
SUCCESSFULLY.

366
00:20:50,791 --> 00:20:53,878
YOU'D NOT ONLY BE PLACING
SURAK'S<i> KATRA</i> IN JEOPARDY --

367
00:20:53,878 --> 00:20:55,379
YOU COULD KILL ARCHER.

368
00:20:55,379 --> 00:20:57,924
THE RISKS ARE ACCEPTABLE.

369
00:20:57,924 --> 00:20:59,425
I DOUBT SURAK WOULD AGREE.

370
00:20:59,425 --> 00:21:01,635
WHAT ALTERNATIVE
WOULD YOU SUGGEST --

371
00:21:01,635 --> 00:21:03,930
THAT WE FOLLOW THIS HUMAN?

372
00:21:03,930 --> 00:21:05,890
I BELIEVE
YOUR PREJUDICE TOWARDS HUMANS

373
00:21:05,890 --> 00:21:07,433
IS CLOUDING YOUR JUDGMENT.

374
00:21:07,433 --> 00:21:09,435
YOU QUESTIONING MY LOGIC?

375
00:21:09,435 --> 00:21:11,938
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

376
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:17,443
Syrran chose to place the<i> katra</i>
in Archer.

377
00:21:17,443 --> 00:21:18,903
He must have had his reasons,

378
00:21:18,903 --> 00:21:21,321
even if we don't understand
them.

379
00:21:21,321 --> 00:21:24,324
The reason is obvious.
He was dying.

380
00:21:24,324 --> 00:21:26,493
Your daughter couldn't reach him
in time.

381
00:21:26,493 --> 00:21:28,537
He had to choose Archer.

382
00:21:28,537 --> 00:21:30,581
That may be.

383
00:21:30,581 --> 00:21:31,916
But we do have a choice.

384
00:21:31,916 --> 00:21:34,961
Now, for the sake
of everyone involved,

385
00:21:34,961 --> 00:21:37,504
I ask you to reconsider.

386
00:21:37,504 --> 00:21:39,257
I've made my decision.

387
00:21:39,257 --> 00:21:42,093
I'll perform the procedure
in one hour.

388
00:21:43,177 --> 00:21:44,971
And if Archer dies?

389
00:21:44,971 --> 00:21:49,516
I won't sacrifice our future to
protect the life of one human.

390
00:22:00,569 --> 00:22:02,905
YOU KNOW...

391
00:22:04,406 --> 00:22:07,618
...I'M THE ONE
WITH A VULCAN GHOST IN HIS HEAD,

392
00:22:07,618 --> 00:22:09,912
DEPENDING ON WHO YOU BELIEVE.

393
00:22:11,622 --> 00:22:16,627
BUT...I DON'T FEEL
HALF AS BAD AS YOU LOOK.

394
00:22:18,879 --> 00:22:21,632
I'M CONSIDERING OUR OPTIONS.

395
00:22:23,134 --> 00:22:25,219
AT LEAST WE KNOW
YOUR MOTHER'S OKAY.

396
00:22:26,887 --> 00:22:32,601
SHE'S JOINED A VIOLENT CULT.
SHE'S NOT OKAY.

397
00:22:32,601 --> 00:22:36,563
I DON'T THINK THESE PEOPLE HAD
ANYTHING TO DO WITH THE EMBASSY.

398
00:22:36,563 --> 00:22:38,398
YOU SOUND CONVINCED.

399
00:22:39,942 --> 00:22:43,070
LET'S JUST SAY
IT'S MORE THAN A GUT FEELING.

400
00:22:44,488 --> 00:22:45,823
[ DOOR CREAKS OPEN ]

401
00:22:48,993 --> 00:22:51,745
WE'VE COME TO A DECISION.

402
00:22:51,745 --> 00:22:53,664
THE<i> KATRA</i> MUST BE REMOVED.

403
00:22:55,041 --> 00:22:56,834
I CAN'T ARGUE WITH THAT.

404
00:22:56,834 --> 00:23:00,087
THERE'S A PROCEDURE, A RITUAL.

405
00:23:00,087 --> 00:23:02,673
IT WILL TRANSFER
THE<i> KATRA</i> TO ANOTHER PERSON.

406
00:23:02,673 --> 00:23:04,591
IT'S NOT WITHOUT RISK.

407
00:23:04,591 --> 00:23:07,803
VULCAN NEUROLOGY
IS EXCEPTIONALLY RESILIENT,

408
00:23:07,803 --> 00:23:09,429
BUT A HUMAN'S...

409
00:23:09,429 --> 00:23:12,850
THE SHOCK TO YOUR
NERVOUS SYSTEM WILL BE SEVERE.

410
00:23:12,850 --> 00:23:14,560
IT COULD KILL YOU.

411
00:23:14,560 --> 00:23:16,020
YOU MUST DECLINE.

412
00:23:16,020 --> 00:23:18,396
WE'RE NOT OFFERING A CHOICE.

413
00:23:19,773 --> 00:23:21,483
YOU'D DO THIS BY FORCE?

414
00:23:21,483 --> 00:23:25,029
WE'D PREFER THAT YOU UNDERTAKE
THE RITUAL WILLINGLY.

415
00:23:25,029 --> 00:23:27,281
IT WILL STAND
A BETTER CHANCE OF SUCCESS.

416
00:23:27,281 --> 00:23:31,827
HOWEVER, IF FORCE IS REQUIRED,
WE WON'T HESITATE TO USE IT.

417
00:23:36,332 --> 00:23:37,750
LET'S GET STARTED.

418
00:23:37,750 --> 00:23:38,751
CAPTAIN.

419
00:23:38,751 --> 00:23:40,586
IT'S MY CALL.

420
00:23:44,048 --> 00:23:45,383
ADMIRAL GARDNER FOLLOWED

421
00:23:45,383 --> 00:23:46,717
THE VULCAN LINE
STRAIGHT DOWN THE MIDDLE.

422
00:23:46,717 --> 00:23:48,635
HE WANTS US OUT OF HERE
YESTERDAY.

423
00:23:48,635 --> 00:23:50,763
DID YOU TELL HIM
ABOUT THE CAPTAIN AND T'POL?

424
00:23:50,763 --> 00:23:52,514
I LEFT THAT PART OUT.

425
00:23:52,514 --> 00:23:54,141
<i>ENTERPRISE</i> WAS SUPPOSED
TO LEAVE ORBIT AN HOUR AGO.

426
00:23:54,141 --> 00:23:55,684
V'LAS IS NOT A PATIENT MAN.

427
00:23:55,684 --> 00:23:57,561
THERE'S NOT A WHOLE LOT
HE CAN DO ABOUT IT.

428
00:24:01,065 --> 00:24:03,192
-HELL OF A JOB, TRAVIS.
-THANK YOU, SIR.

429
00:24:03,192 --> 00:24:04,651
JUST FIND THEM
AND BRING THEM BACK --

430
00:24:04,651 --> 00:24:07,654
-NO SIGHTSEEING ALONG THE WAY.
-UNDERSTOOD.

431
00:24:07,654 --> 00:24:10,908
WE'VE GOT A RECON SATELLITE
TO JAM.

432
00:24:10,908 --> 00:24:12,868
<i>Enterprise</i> hasn't left orbit.

433
00:24:12,868 --> 00:24:15,662
They're maintaining a stationary
position above The Forge.

434
00:24:15,662 --> 00:24:17,623
[ SIGHS ]
KEEP MONITORING THEM.

435
00:24:17,623 --> 00:24:19,666
-Yes, Excellency.
-[ BEEPING ]

436
00:24:19,666 --> 00:24:21,919
WE CAN'T PROCEED
WITH THE OPERATION

437
00:24:21,919 --> 00:24:23,837
WHILE THE EARTH SHIP IS THERE.

438
00:24:23,837 --> 00:24:26,006
YOU'RE CONCERNED
ABOUT WITNESSES.

439
00:24:26,006 --> 00:24:28,175
GARDNER GAVE THEM
AN ORDER TO LEAVE.

440
00:24:28,175 --> 00:24:30,303
I HEARD THE TRANSMISSION.

441
00:24:30,303 --> 00:24:32,972
SO NOW WE'RE MONITORING
THEIR COMMUNICATIONS?

442
00:24:32,972 --> 00:24:36,976
THEY WOULDN'T DISOBEY AN ORDER
WITHOUT A REASON.

443
00:24:36,976 --> 00:24:39,728
I INTEND TO FIND OUT WHAT IT IS.

444
00:24:39,728 --> 00:24:41,772
[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

445
00:24:51,698 --> 00:24:53,951
PASSED DOWN THROUGH THE AGES,

446
00:24:53,951 --> 00:24:57,288
THE<i> KATRA</i> OF SURAK...

447
00:24:57,288 --> 00:24:59,957
FATHER OF ALL WE HOLD TRUE,

448
00:24:59,957 --> 00:25:02,542
LIVES ON IN THIS MAN.

449
00:25:09,049 --> 00:25:13,804
LET IT NOW...LIVE ON IN ME.

450
00:25:20,769 --> 00:25:23,314
[ SPEAKING VULCAN ]

451
00:25:56,805 --> 00:25:58,765
SURAK.

452
00:25:58,765 --> 00:26:01,018
[ GRUNTING ]

453
00:26:04,897 --> 00:26:07,900
GOOD TO SEE YOU AGAIN, CAPTAIN.

454
00:26:07,900 --> 00:26:10,903
MY APPEARANCE MUST BE
QUITE DISCONCERTING.

455
00:26:10,903 --> 00:26:11,945
I APOLOGIZE.

456
00:26:11,945 --> 00:26:14,114
RADIATION SICKNESS?

457
00:26:14,114 --> 00:26:17,951
WE'RE PAYING A HEAVY PRICE
FOR OUR FOOLISHNESS.

458
00:26:17,951 --> 00:26:21,080
LOGIC HAS NOT WON THIS DAY...

459
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:24,666
BUT THIS DAY WON'T LAST FOREVER.

460
00:26:24,666 --> 00:26:28,879
LOGIC IS AT THE HEART
OF EVERY VULCAN.

461
00:26:28,879 --> 00:26:31,006
EVEN AS THE ASHES FALL,

462
00:26:31,006 --> 00:26:34,260
MY PEOPLE ARE DISCOVERING
A NEW WAY.

463
00:26:34,260 --> 00:26:37,971
YOU CAN ACCOMPLISH
WHAT SYRRAN COULD NOT.

464
00:26:37,971 --> 00:26:40,558
BUT SYRRAN...

465
00:26:40,558 --> 00:26:42,809
WAS A VULCAN.

466
00:26:42,809 --> 00:26:45,062
AND YOU'RE HUMAN...

467
00:26:45,062 --> 00:26:47,273
WHICH MEANS
YOU ARE UNTOUCHED BY A CULTURE

468
00:26:47,273 --> 00:26:51,360
THAT CAN NO LONGER SEE
ITS OWN IMMINENT DESTRUCTION.

469
00:26:51,360 --> 00:26:54,071
I CANNOT LET WHAT HAPPENED
TO THE VULCANS OF MY TIME

470
00:26:54,071 --> 00:26:56,240
TAKE PLACE AGAIN.

471
00:26:59,034 --> 00:27:02,620
FIND WHAT MY PEOPLE HAVE LOST.

472
00:27:02,620 --> 00:27:04,664
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

473
00:27:06,875 --> 00:27:08,210
[ GROANING ]

474
00:27:08,210 --> 00:27:12,005
FIND THE<i> KIR'SHARA.</i>

475
00:27:13,840 --> 00:27:15,593
[ GASPING ]

476
00:27:16,885 --> 00:27:18,596
CAPTAIN.

477
00:27:19,972 --> 00:27:21,765
I FAILED.

478
00:27:21,765 --> 00:27:22,975
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

479
00:27:25,144 --> 00:27:27,854
SURAK CHOOSES
TO REMAIN WHERE HE IS.

480
00:27:44,580 --> 00:27:46,457
-THE SATELLITE'S BEEN DISABLED.
-[ BEEPING ]

481
00:27:46,457 --> 00:27:48,875
THEY'VE GOT 6 MINUTES
TO GET THROUGH.

482
00:27:48,875 --> 00:27:51,337
TRAVIS...IT'S ALL YOURS.

483
00:27:54,590 --> 00:27:57,551
PROBABLY SHOULD HAVE SKIPPED
BREAKFAST THIS MORNING.

484
00:27:57,551 --> 00:27:58,969
[ BEEPING ]

485
00:27:58,969 --> 00:28:00,929
-THEY'RE THROUGH.
-WE'RE LOSING CONTACT.

486
00:28:00,929 --> 00:28:04,642
THESE THERMALS
ARE ONLY GOING TO GET STRONGER.

487
00:28:04,642 --> 00:28:05,767
[ THUDDING ]

488
00:28:05,767 --> 00:28:09,104
THAT WAS NO THERMAL.
[ GRUNTS ]

489
00:28:15,693 --> 00:28:17,737
THE PLASMA CANNONS
ARE STILL WORKING,

490
00:28:17,737 --> 00:28:20,240
BUT I CAN'T SAY THE SAME
FOR THE TARGETING SENSORS.

491
00:28:20,240 --> 00:28:23,285
WE MUST BE GETTING CLOSE
TO THE GEOMAGNETIC FIELD.

492
00:28:24,702 --> 00:28:26,330
IT DOESN'T SEEM
TO BE AFFECTING THEM.

493
00:28:26,330 --> 00:28:28,499
THEY MUST HAVE
BETTER SHIELDING.

494
00:28:28,499 --> 00:28:32,169
I'LL HAVE TO AIM MANUALLY.
CAN YOU GET US ON THEIR TAIL?

495
00:28:35,631 --> 00:28:37,216
[ GRUNTING ]

496
00:28:42,513 --> 00:28:45,265
HOW ARE THEY STILL BELOW US?

497
00:28:45,265 --> 00:28:47,685
WE'VE LOST
PART OF THE STARBOARD WING.

498
00:28:47,685 --> 00:28:50,563
-WE HAVE TO ABORT.
-I THINK I CAN GET US DOWN.

499
00:28:50,563 --> 00:28:52,606
YOU WON'T BE ABLE
TO GET US BACK UP.

500
00:28:52,606 --> 00:28:54,608
-[ BEEPING ]
-THRUSTERS ARE OFF-LINE.

501
00:28:54,608 --> 00:28:57,653
WE'LL HAVE TO FIRE
THE CHEMICAL ROCKETS. HANG ON.

502
00:28:57,653 --> 00:28:59,988
[ BEEPING ]

503
00:28:59,988 --> 00:29:01,990
THEY'VE BEEN FIRED ON.

504
00:29:01,990 --> 00:29:04,159
THEY TOOK DAMAGE, BUT THEY'RE
HEADING BACK TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

505
00:29:04,159 --> 00:29:05,661
I GUESS 6 MINUTES
WASN'T ENOUGH.

506
00:29:05,661 --> 00:29:07,871
THEY MUST
HAVE BEEN MONITORING US.

507
00:29:07,871 --> 00:29:09,998
THREE SHIPS CLOSING
ON OUR POSITION.

508
00:29:09,998 --> 00:29:11,917
[ BEEPING ]

509
00:29:11,917 --> 00:29:14,420
WE'RE BEING HAILED.
IT'S ADMINISTRATOR V'LAS.

510
00:29:16,672 --> 00:29:18,549
<i>WHY DID YOU LAUNCH</i>
<i>A SHUTTLEPOD?</i>

511
00:29:18,549 --> 00:29:20,384
WHY THE HELL
DID YOU FIRE ON IT?

512
00:29:20,384 --> 00:29:22,969
<i>YOU HAD NO AUTHORIZATION.</i>
<i>ANSWER THE QUESTION.</i>

513
00:29:22,969 --> 00:29:25,347
WE'RE LOOKING FOR OUR CAPTAIN.

514
00:29:25,347 --> 00:29:27,683
<i>ARCHER'S ON THE SURFACE?</i>

515
00:29:27,683 --> 00:29:30,977
HE'S IN THE FORGE,
SEARCHING FOR THE SYRRANNITES.

516
00:29:30,977 --> 00:29:34,064
<i>YOU WERE ORDERED</i>
<i>TO LEAVE ORBIT.</i>

517
00:29:35,107 --> 00:29:37,317
I ADVISED THEM TO STAY.

518
00:29:38,527 --> 00:29:40,112
<i>I ASSUME YOU ASSISTED</i>

519
00:29:40,112 --> 00:29:42,989
<i>IN DISABLING</i>
<i>THE SECURITY SATELLITE.</i>

520
00:29:42,989 --> 00:29:45,033
I GAVE THEM THE CODE.

521
00:29:48,036 --> 00:29:50,830
<i>COMMANDER TUCKER...</i>

522
00:29:50,830 --> 00:29:53,166
<i>YOU'RE TO BREAK ORBIT</i>
<i>IMMEDIATELY.</i>

523
00:29:53,166 --> 00:29:55,377
WE'RE NOT LEAVING
WITHOUT THE CAPTAIN.

524
00:29:55,377 --> 00:29:57,755
<i>YOU WILL LEAVE IMMEDIATELY</i>

525
00:29:57,755 --> 00:30:02,092
<i>OR I'LL ORDER MY SHIPS</i>
<i>TO OPEN FIRE.</i>

526
00:30:20,902 --> 00:30:22,655
HOW IS HE?

527
00:30:25,157 --> 00:30:28,577
HIS BREATHING HAS STABILIZED...

528
00:30:28,577 --> 00:30:30,912
BUT HIS FEVER IS STILL HIGH.

529
00:30:34,833 --> 00:30:36,669
HE AGREED TO THE RITUAL.

530
00:30:38,337 --> 00:30:40,589
IF HE HADN'T,
YOU WOULD HAVE FORCED HIM.

531
00:30:43,383 --> 00:30:45,927
YOU CLAIM THAT SURAK'S TEACHINGS
HAVE BEEN CORRUPTED

532
00:30:45,927 --> 00:30:47,053
BY THE HIGH COMMAND...

533
00:30:48,180 --> 00:30:50,182
...BUT YOU'RE NO DIFFERENT.

534
00:30:50,182 --> 00:30:52,225
THERE IS
A PROFOUND DIFFERENCE.

535
00:30:52,225 --> 00:30:54,102
YOU DECEIVE YOURSELF.

536
00:30:54,102 --> 00:30:56,188
T'POL.

537
00:30:58,607 --> 00:31:02,235
I SHOULDN'T HAVE COME HERE
LOOKING FOR YOU.

538
00:31:02,235 --> 00:31:04,988
AND I DON'T WANT
ANYTHING MORE TO DO WITH YOU.

539
00:31:07,073 --> 00:31:09,201
IF THAT'S YOUR WISH.

540
00:31:14,414 --> 00:31:15,957
HOW LONG HAVE I BEEN OUT?

541
00:31:15,957 --> 00:31:17,250
MORE THAN 3 HOURS.

542
00:31:18,752 --> 00:31:20,796
I FEEL LIKE

543
00:31:20,796 --> 00:31:24,842
I JUST PULLED MY HEAD
OUT OF A PLASMA RELAY.

544
00:31:25,801 --> 00:31:27,010
YOU SHOULD REST.

545
00:31:27,010 --> 00:31:29,054
[ SIGHING ]

546
00:31:41,066 --> 00:31:42,860
THE<i> KIR'SHARA.</i>

547
00:31:43,985 --> 00:31:46,029
WHAT DO YOU KNOW ABOUT IT?

548
00:31:46,029 --> 00:31:48,281
IT WAS IMPORTANT TO SURAK.

549
00:31:50,659 --> 00:31:51,869
AND IT'S IN THERE.

550
00:31:52,828 --> 00:31:54,413
WHAT'S A<i> KIR'SHARA?</i>

551
00:31:54,413 --> 00:31:56,790
AN ARTIFACT --
SYRRAN LED US HERE TO FIND IT.

552
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:58,876
IF HE KNOWS WHERE IT IS...

553
00:31:58,876 --> 00:32:00,878
TELESCOPES HAVE SIGHTED
THREE VULCAN CRUISERS

554
00:32:00,878 --> 00:32:02,421
IN ORBIT OVER THE FORGE.

555
00:32:02,421 --> 00:32:04,130
THE HIGH COMMAND KNOWS
WE'RE HERE.

556
00:32:04,130 --> 00:32:06,675
WE SHOULD EVACUATE
IMMEDIATELY.

557
00:32:06,675 --> 00:32:08,427
GIVE THE ORDER.

558
00:32:11,054 --> 00:32:12,431
I CAN FIND IT.

559
00:32:14,307 --> 00:32:15,975
[ RUMBLING, BEEPING ]

560
00:32:15,975 --> 00:32:18,812
THAT ONE MISSED US
BY 20 METERS.

561
00:32:18,812 --> 00:32:22,649
TACTICAL ALERT.
POLARIZE HULL PLATING.

562
00:32:22,649 --> 00:32:25,944
HOW MANY WARNING SHOTS
DO VULCANS USUALLY FIRE?

563
00:32:25,944 --> 00:32:26,945
NONE.

564
00:32:26,945 --> 00:32:27,905
[ BEEPING ]

565
00:32:27,905 --> 00:32:29,406
V'LAS.

566
00:32:31,950 --> 00:32:35,120
<i>I'M RUNNING OUT OF PATIENCE,</i>
<i>COMMANDER.</i>

567
00:32:35,120 --> 00:32:36,830
WE'VE BEEN OVER THIS.

568
00:32:36,830 --> 00:32:39,750
OUR CAPTAIN AND FIRST OFFICER
ARE DOWN THERE.

569
00:32:39,750 --> 00:32:43,420
<i>WE'LL MAKE SURE</i>
<i>THEY'RE RETURNED TO YOU.</i>

570
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:46,005
<i>BREAK ORBIT -- NOW.</i>

571
00:32:46,005 --> 00:32:47,173
[ BEEPS ]

572
00:32:48,425 --> 00:32:50,636
YOU REALLY THINK HE'LL DO IT?

573
00:32:50,636 --> 00:32:54,723
V'LAS WILL DO WHATEVER IT TAKES
TO ACCOMPLISH HIS GOAL.

574
00:32:57,434 --> 00:33:00,479
VULCAN AND EARTH HAVE BEEN
ALLIES FOR A HUNDRED YEARS.

575
00:33:00,479 --> 00:33:03,022
SYRRANNITES MUST HAVE SEEN
OUR SHIPS BY NOW.

576
00:33:03,022 --> 00:33:04,691
IF THEY EVACUATE INTO THE FORGE,

577
00:33:04,691 --> 00:33:06,902
THEY'LL BE
EXTREMELY HARD TO TRACK.

578
00:33:06,902 --> 00:33:08,946
WE CAN'T WAIT ANY LONGER.

579
00:33:08,946 --> 00:33:10,697
[ BEEPING ]

580
00:33:10,697 --> 00:33:13,575
DRIVE<i> ENTERPRISE</i> FROM ORBIT.
USE ALL NECESSARY FORCE.

581
00:33:13,575 --> 00:33:16,244
Yes, Excellency.

582
00:33:21,040 --> 00:33:22,250
[ ALARM BLARING ]

583
00:33:22,250 --> 00:33:24,670
PHASE CANNONS, RETURN FIRE.

584
00:33:26,546 --> 00:33:29,883
THE VULCAN SHIPS
ARE FIRING ON<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

585
00:33:29,883 --> 00:33:31,426
-WE COULD BE NEXT.
-[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

586
00:33:31,426 --> 00:33:32,928
TAKE CHARGE OF THE EVACUATION.

587
00:33:32,928 --> 00:33:34,847
WE'LL MEET YOU ON THE FORGE
AS SOON AS WE CAN.

588
00:33:34,847 --> 00:33:36,598
YOU CAN'T STAY HERE.

589
00:33:36,598 --> 00:33:39,309
I'VE SPENT TWO YEARS
SEARCHING FOR THE ARTIFACT.

590
00:33:39,309 --> 00:33:42,312
IF THERE'S A CHANCE
OF FINDING IT...

591
00:33:42,312 --> 00:33:43,814
T'POL?

592
00:33:45,565 --> 00:33:46,859
I'M STAYING.

593
00:33:47,985 --> 00:33:50,069
GO.

594
00:33:50,069 --> 00:33:52,113
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

595
00:34:07,629 --> 00:34:09,673
-[ ALARM BLARING ]
-[ GRUNTS ]

596
00:34:09,673 --> 00:34:11,967
RE-ROUTE EMERGENCY POWER
TO PHASE CANNONS.

597
00:34:11,967 --> 00:34:13,886
HULL BREACH ON C-DECK.

598
00:34:13,886 --> 00:34:15,470
THEY'RE REPORTING CASUALTIES.

599
00:34:15,470 --> 00:34:18,015
-[ BEEPING ]
-V'LAS IS HAILING, AUDIO ONLY.

600
00:34:18,015 --> 00:34:18,974
PUT HIM THROUGH.

601
00:34:18,974 --> 00:34:20,266
[ BEEPING ]

602
00:34:20,266 --> 00:34:22,477
You're hopelessly outgunned.

603
00:34:22,477 --> 00:34:25,438
Weapons are off-line,
engines failing.

604
00:34:25,438 --> 00:34:28,441
Don't force me
to destroy your ship.

605
00:34:28,441 --> 00:34:29,693
[ BEEPS ]

606
00:34:29,693 --> 00:34:33,071
HE'S RIGHT.
WE SHOULD WITHDRAW.

607
00:34:33,071 --> 00:34:36,033
OUR DEATHS WON'T HELP
CAPTAIN ARCHER OR T'POL.

608
00:34:38,284 --> 00:34:40,829
GET US THE HELL OUT OF HERE.

609
00:34:40,829 --> 00:34:44,457
THE MOMENT<i> ENTERPRISE</i>
IS BEYOND SCANNER RANGE,

610
00:34:44,457 --> 00:34:47,210
BEGIN BOMBARDMENT
OF THE COMPOUND.

611
00:34:47,210 --> 00:34:48,712
Yes, Excellency.

612
00:34:48,712 --> 00:34:50,213
[ BEEPING ]

613
00:35:18,075 --> 00:35:20,201
T'KLAAS --

614
00:35:20,201 --> 00:35:24,790
HE WAS A STUDENT OF SURAK, ONE
OF THE FIRST<i> KOLINAHR</i> MASTERS.

615
00:35:27,375 --> 00:35:29,962
THERE'S NO INSCRIPTION,

616
00:35:29,962 --> 00:35:32,464
NOTHING TO INDICATE
HIS BLOODLINE.

617
00:35:32,464 --> 00:35:34,883
HOW DO YOU KNOW HIS NAME?

618
00:35:36,384 --> 00:35:37,970
WE'RE GETTING CLOSE.

619
00:35:37,970 --> 00:35:40,179
[ EXPLOSIONS ]

620
00:35:40,179 --> 00:35:42,390
THEY'VE BEGUN THEIR ASSAULT.

621
00:35:49,147 --> 00:35:52,109
[ EXPLOSIONS ]

622
00:35:52,109 --> 00:35:54,444
IT'S HERE.

623
00:36:28,186 --> 00:36:30,396
[ EXPLOSIONS ]

624
00:36:40,490 --> 00:36:43,368
I HAD MY DOUBTS
WHETHER IT REALLY EXISTED.

625
00:36:43,368 --> 00:36:44,661
[ EXPLOSION ]

626
00:36:47,580 --> 00:36:49,207
LET'S GO.

627
00:36:50,834 --> 00:36:52,293
[ EXPLOSIONS ]

628
00:36:52,293 --> 00:36:54,546
[ GRUNTING ]

629
00:36:56,131 --> 00:36:57,757
THIS WAY.

630
00:37:04,764 --> 00:37:06,432
REPORT.

631
00:37:06,432 --> 00:37:09,061
Geomagnetic interference --
we can't get a target lock.

632
00:37:09,061 --> 00:37:11,312
BLANKET THE AREA.

633
00:37:11,312 --> 00:37:13,773
[ EXPLOSIONS ]

634
00:37:47,099 --> 00:37:49,184
[ GRUNTING ]

635
00:37:49,184 --> 00:37:51,186
[ ALL PANTING ]

636
00:38:07,077 --> 00:38:09,246
The sanctuary's
been destroyed.

637
00:38:09,246 --> 00:38:11,497
COMB THE DESERT.

638
00:38:11,497 --> 00:38:13,499
MAKE SURE
THERE ARE NO SURVIVORS.

639
00:38:13,499 --> 00:38:15,001
Affirmative.

640
00:38:15,001 --> 00:38:17,212
YOU'RE PRESIDING OVER
A MASSACRE.

641
00:38:17,212 --> 00:38:20,381
WE ARE ELIMINATING A THREAT.

642
00:38:24,302 --> 00:38:25,678
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

643
00:38:27,346 --> 00:38:29,224
I'M FINE.

644
00:38:29,224 --> 00:38:31,935
WE SHOULD KEEP MOVING.

645
00:38:39,943 --> 00:38:43,321
-[ GROANING ]
-CAPTAIN.

646
00:38:50,120 --> 00:38:52,164
[ GROANING ]

647
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:11,724
I WAS AFRAID
YOU WERE STILL INSIDE.

648
00:39:13,434 --> 00:39:14,936
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

649
00:39:16,437 --> 00:39:18,439
WE FOUND THE<i> KIR'SHARA.</i>

650
00:39:21,693 --> 00:39:25,030
YOU HAVE ALWAYS STRUGGLED SO
WITH YOUR EMOTIONS.

651
00:39:26,198 --> 00:39:27,949
I CAME HERE...

652
00:39:27,949 --> 00:39:30,409
I DID ALL THIS TO HELP YOU.

653
00:39:30,409 --> 00:39:32,996
[ GROANS ]

654
00:39:32,996 --> 00:39:34,914
[ Voice breaking ]
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

655
00:39:34,914 --> 00:39:36,958
YOU WILL.

656
00:39:39,294 --> 00:39:40,378
[ CRYING ]

657
00:39:40,378 --> 00:39:42,214
MOTHER...

658
00:39:45,133 --> 00:39:50,055
I'VE ALWAYS BEEN SO PROUD
OF YOU...MY T'POL.

659
00:39:53,516 --> 00:39:54,976
[ SNIFFLES ]

660
00:39:57,395 --> 00:39:58,521
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

661
00:39:58,521 --> 00:40:00,523
MOTHER.

662
00:40:07,030 --> 00:40:09,074
[ SNIFFLES ]

663
00:40:15,163 --> 00:40:17,749
I UNDERSTAND
WE SUFFERED CASUALTIES.

664
00:40:17,749 --> 00:40:21,294
INJURIES, TWO OF THEM SERIOUS.

665
00:40:21,294 --> 00:40:24,505
I SHARE YOUR CONCERN
ABOUT CAPTAIN ARCHER AND T'POL.

666
00:40:24,505 --> 00:40:26,674
THEY'VE BEEN IN TOUGH JAMS
BEFORE.

667
00:40:28,885 --> 00:40:31,429
WHAT DOES THE HIGH COMMAND HAVE
AGAINST THE SYRRANNITES?

668
00:40:31,429 --> 00:40:34,557
THEY WENT TO A LOT OF TROUBLE
TO FRAME THEM

669
00:40:34,557 --> 00:40:35,850
FOR THE EMBASSY BOMBING.

670
00:40:35,850 --> 00:40:37,310
THE SYRRANNITES
BELIEVE VIOLENCE

671
00:40:37,310 --> 00:40:40,230
TO BE ANTITHETICAL
TO SURAK'S TEACHINGS.

672
00:40:40,230 --> 00:40:42,232
SO THEY'RE PACIFISTS.

673
00:40:42,232 --> 00:40:44,650
V'LAS CONSIDERS THAT
A DANGEROUS MIND-SET,

674
00:40:44,650 --> 00:40:46,444
PARTICULARLY NOW.

675
00:40:46,444 --> 00:40:47,987
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

676
00:40:49,572 --> 00:40:51,908
THE HIGH COMMAND IS PLANNING
TO ATTACK ANDORIA.

677
00:40:51,908 --> 00:40:53,952
WAIT. WAIT.

678
00:40:53,952 --> 00:40:57,789
VULCAN AND ANDORIA SIGNED
A PEACE TREATY TWO YEARS AGO.

679
00:40:57,789 --> 00:40:59,498
CAPTAIN ARCHER
HELPED NEGOTIATE IT.

680
00:40:59,498 --> 00:41:01,918
VULCAN INTELLIGENCE CLAIMS

681
00:41:01,918 --> 00:41:04,296
THE ANDORIANS
ARE DEVELOPING A WEAPON,

682
00:41:04,296 --> 00:41:06,339
POSSIBLY BASED
ON XINDI TECHNOLOGY.

683
00:41:06,339 --> 00:41:08,633
AND YOU DON'T BELIEVE IT.

684
00:41:08,633 --> 00:41:11,510
I SUSPECT V'LAS IS USING
THE CLAIM TO ADVANCE AN AGENDA.

685
00:41:11,510 --> 00:41:15,223
HE'S PERSUADED THE HIGH COMMAND
TO LAUNCH A PREEMPTIVE STRIKE.

686
00:41:15,223 --> 00:41:17,976
HE'S GONNA START
AN INTERSTELLAR WAR.

687
00:41:17,976 --> 00:41:21,062
ONE THAT COULD DEVASTATE
ANDORIA AND VULCAN,

688
00:41:21,062 --> 00:41:24,399
AND EVENTUALLY INVOLVE
OTHER WORLDS...

689
00:41:24,399 --> 00:41:26,276
